Jarl is a Perl/Tk application that allows one to access a Jabber
account and have full access to the Jabber IM system.  It runs on any
platform that supports Perl and Tk, which at this time is most
platforms.

Jarl is going to be a full featured Jabber client that supports 100%
of the features that the Jabber IM offers.

WWW: http://jarl.sourceforge.net/
